            <h1>About JobSpark</h1>
            <p>JobSpark is an innovative job portal designed to simplify and streamline the hiring process for both job seekers and recruiters. Whether you're a fresh graduate seeking your first opportunity or a company looking for top talent, JobSpark provides a smart, user-friendly platform to connect the right people with the right jobs.</p>
        </div>
