            <h2>For Job Seekers:</h2>
            <p>JobSpark allows candidates to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Create detailed profiles with resumes, skills, and goals</li>
                <li>Apply to relevant job opportunities with a single click</li>
                <li>Track application status and interview calls</li>
                <li>Receive automated recommendations based on their profile</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="about-block" style="--delay:0.4s;">
            <h2>For Recruiters:</h2>
            <p>Recruiters can access a powerful Admin Panel to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Post job openings and manage applications</li>
                <li>View and filter candidate profiles using advanced search tools</li>
                <li>Schedule and manage interviews</li>
                <li>Make data-driven hiring decisions with analytics and insights</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="about-block" style="--delay:0.6s;">
            <h2>Why JobSpark?</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Easy-to-use interface for both job seekers and recruiters</li>
                <li>Secure and efficient platform for managing job applications</li>
                <li>Automation tools to reduce manual hiring efforts</li>
                <li>Built to support final-year students, freshers, and experienced professionals</li>
            </ul>
            <p>At JobSpark, we aim to ignite careers and accelerate recruitment by bridging the gap between talent and opportunity.</p>
        </div>
